{"id": 2195, "genre": 1000, "title": "即便是处在亲密关系中，你觉得哪些事情还需要保持独立？", "description": "对你来说，哪些方面的“自我”更重要一些？（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 54954, "comment_count": 86, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180226155450PiBQNIe62F3xJWkO.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-02-26T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 3780, "title": "即便是处在亲密关系中，你觉得哪些事情还需要保持独立？", "content": "即便是处在亲密关系中，你觉得哪些事情还需要保持独立？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 267248, "content": "维持或拓展社交圈，不因为恋爱或结婚疏远其他朋友", "image": "img/option/option/20180226164832PpFo3GyjI6D1HiKL.gif", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 267253, "content": "共同的经济开销商量着来，不完全依赖其中一方", "image": "img/option/option/20180226164950K5BSPFgGIlQ4JiXZ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 267254, "content": "有不同看法的时候，不用“价值观必须一致”互相压制", "image": "img/option/option/20180226165106Whae0r7lOXNCgQTw.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 267255, "content": "保留各自的兴趣爱好", "image": "img/option/option/20180226165315z9aNKp52syfXCDtT.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 267257, "content": "有可以自由支配的独处时间", "image": "img/option/option/201802261726297KqNu5RGEQbykY3V.gif", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 267258, "content": "能接受对方不是每次都及时回信息，没有“秒回强迫症”", "image": "img/option/option/20180226172924b2IpLFV8otXYkvi0.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 267259, "content": "社交网络上不用发啥都捎带上对方", "image": "img/option/option/20180226173137zixaQPMSwIfTbLse.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 267260, "content": "不干涉对方的职业选择", "image": "img/option/option/20180226173324aMwTYs2IJ6kfGAKq.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}